title: Greg Stone: Bad Feet
description:
Kippy and Foley are back for a fun one with old pal Greg Stone. The boys answer your garbage questions from Patreon. Its a hoot! Thanks for listening. Love youse guys.

Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE. Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the test.
